OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772993165
OL,3,CVictim of alleged rape by teenagers
OL,4,Ctells court 'I never said yeah'
OL,6,FA teenage girl alleged to have been
OL,7,Fraped by three schoolboys broke down
OL,8,Fin tears as she told barristers "I
OL,9,Fnever said yeah".
OL,11,FManchester's Minshull Street Crown
OL,12,FCourt heard the three boys, then aged
OL,13,F12, 13, and 14, allegedly "took it in
OL,14,Fturns" to rape the then 13-year-old
OL,15,Fgirl in bushes close to the Newbold
OL,16,FTram Stop in Rochdale in February 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772993165
OL,3,CVictim of alleged rape by teenagers
OL,4,Ctells court 'I never said yeah'
OL,6,FThe three boys, who cannot be named
OL,7,Fbecause of their ages, deny the
OL,8,Fcharges they face. Two, now aged 15
OL,9,Fand 16, are standing trial. The third,
OL,10,Fwho was aged 12 at the time and is now
OL,11,F14, has been deemed unfit to stand
OL,12,Ftrial.
OL,14,FThe alleged victim also cannot be
OL,15,Fnamed.
OL,17,FJurors were shown a pre-recorded video
OL,18,Fof the girl being cross examined by
OL,19,Fdefence and prosecution barristers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772993165
OL,3,CVictim of alleged rape by teenagers
OL,4,Ctells court 'I never said yeah'
OL,6,FIn the video, the girl said she knew
OL,7,Ftwo of the boys but did not know them
OL,8,Fpersonally, and denied flirting with
OL,9,Fany of them.
OL,11,FThe girl said the now 15-year-old put
OL,12,Fhis arm around her as she got off a
OL,13,Ftram at Newbold, which made her "quite
OL,14,Funcomfortable".
OL,16,FRachel Shenton, representing the now
OL,17,F15-year-old, asked: "What did you do
OL,18,Fwhen he put his arm around you?"
OL,20,FThe girl replied: "I looked back at
OL,21,F(my friend) to see what she was doing."
OL,26,@}D@Apm}D@Kpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772993165
OL,3,CVictim of alleged rape by teenagers
OL,4,Ctells court 'I never said yeah'
OL,6,FShe said she carried on walking but
OL,7,Fthe 15-year-old walked her into the
OL,8,Fbushes with his arm around her.
OL,10,FPhilip Vollans, representing the now
OL,11,F16-year-old during the cross
OL,12,Fexamination, asked her: "Did you walk
OL,13,Ffreely into the bush?"
OL,15,FThe girl replied: "He led me into the
OL,16,Fbush... It was quite dark. It looked
OL,17,Flike a pathway to me, so I didn't
OL,18,Fnotice."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772993165
OL,3,CVictim of alleged rape by teenagers
OL,4,Ctells court 'I never said yeah'
OL,6,FAsked if she thought the other two
OL,7,Fdefendants were following, she said:
OL,8,F"I personally thought they snuck up
OL,9,Fbehind me. From (my friend's) point of
OL,10,Fview, she said they followed."
OL,12,FJurors heard her say she was 'pushed
OL,13,Fdown' into a bent over position. She
OL,14,Fsaid she couldn't say who was stood
OL,15,Fbehind her, the court heard.
OL,17,FJurors head Ms Shenton ask: "Did you
OL,18,Fsay anything to anyone in the bushes?"
OL,26,@qD@QpmqD@]pn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772993165
OL,3,CVictim of alleged rape by teenagers
OL,4,Ctells court 'I never said yeah'
OL,6,F"No," said the girl, in tears. "Did
OL,7,Fyou scream?" Ms Shenton asked. "No,"
OL,8,Fthe girl said wiping her eyes. "Did
OL,9,Fyou say anything to make the boys
OL,10,Fthink you were all agreeing to it?,"
OL,11,Fshe was asked. "I never said yeah,"
OL,12,Fshe replied.
OL,14,FThe court heard the girl's friend went
OL,15,Finto the bushes and described her as
OL,16,F"looking scared". She said the boys
OL,17,Fthen moved away.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772993165
OL,3,CVictim of alleged rape by teenagers
OL,4,Ctells court 'I never said yeah'
OL,6,FThe jury also heard that at least some
OL,7,Fof the alleged incident was filmed on
OL,8,Fa mobile phone, which was "circulated"
OL,9,Famong the boys and others.
OL,11,FAsked about the alleged incident being
OL,12,Frecorded on a phone, the girl said it
OL,13,Fmade her feel "disgusting".
OL,15,FShe said she did not want to report
OL,16,Fthe matter to her mother or to the
OL,17,Fpolice because she "didn't want to
OL,18,Fcreate a big problem".
OL,20,FShe said: "I just didn't really want
OL,21,Fanyone to find out...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772993165
OL,3,CVictim of alleged rape by teenagers
OL,4,Ctells court 'I never said yeah'
OL,6,F"I eventually agreed and (my friend)
OL,7,Frang my mum off her phone. My mum rang
OL,8,Fthe police. I didn't want the police
OL,9,Fto be involved."
OL,11,FMs Shenton asked: "(The now 15-year-
OL,12,Fold) says you consented to sexual
OL,13,Factivity with him, is he right or
OL,14,Fwrong about that?."
OL,16,FThe girl replied: "He is wrong, I
OL,17,Fdidn't say a word to him. He didn't
OL,18,Fspeak to me."
OL,26,@nD@ZpmnD@dpnsD@TpmtD@Dpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772993165
OL,3,CVictim of alleged rape by teenagers
OL,4,Ctells court 'I never said yeah'
OL,6,FIn re-examination by prosecutor Kim
OL,7,FWhittlestone, the alleged victim was
OL,8,Fasked: "Were two things happening at
OL,9,Fthe same time?"
OL,11,FJurors heard the girl quietly reply:
OL,12,F"Yeah". Asked to elaborate what
OL,13,Fhappened while she was allegedly being
OL,14,Fraped orally, the girl burst into
OL,15,Ftears.
OL,17,FThe court heard her support worker
OL,18,Fasked if she could write down what she
OL,19,Fwas struggling to articulate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772993165
OL,3,CVictim of alleged rape by teenagers
OL,4,Ctells court 'I never said yeah'
OL,6,FOn a post it note, read to the court,
OL,7,Fthe girl wrote: "Someone was putting
OL,8,Ftheir penis inside me from behind."
OL,10,FThe trial was told a friend the girl
OL,11,Fwas with "stepped in to stop what was
OL,12,Fhappening", at which point the now 15
OL,13,Fand 16-year-olds ran away from a scene.
OL,15,FJurors also saw a video interview the
OL,16,Falleged victim's friend gave to the
OL,17,Fpolice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
