OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772993165
OL,3,CVictim of alleged rape by teenagers
OL,4,Ctells court 'I never said yeah'
OL,6,FThe jury heard the friend say: "She
OL,7,Fsaid she didn't want to do it. They
OL,8,Fwent into the bush, they grabbed her
OL,9,Fin the bush. I heard noises. She was
OL,10,Fcrying in the bush.
OL,12,F"I heard one of them say 'let me have
OL,13,Fa go on her'. I went into the bush and
OL,14,Fgrabbed her and they ran off."
OL,16,FThe trial continues.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
